
Visual Quantum Computing Simulator : full state simulator with graphical output, step trace
and PDF dump. Written as a Scala DSL.

VQS G.Ménier 2020 gildas.menier@univ-us.fr
Laboratoire IRISA - Université de Bretagne Sud - France

Scala SBT Project with minimal dependencies (Pdfbox, fontbox and common-loggins)

See the Wiki for some information.



